        "cooked": "<p>That’s good to know about Molly.  I’ll see if I can get Molly working for this use case, and perhaps it will be better overall.</p>\n<p>I don’t carry a mobile device so I can’t use that for my account.  Signal is certainly difficult to use without a mobile device (there were quite a few hiccups registering a new Signal account with Waydroid) but I’m trying to meet people where they’re at so it’s important for me to install.</p>",
