        "created_at": "2025-11-23T06:30:12.618Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Good point; I hadn’t tried that option yet.  However, I did manage to resolve the “Linked devices” issue with the Molly suggestion from <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/reg67\">@reg67</a> - Molly does indeed support manually entering the key in the QR code.  A little bit of qtqr later on the linked device got me the code to manually enter, which succeeded after a couple tries (the QR code on the linked device rotates relatively quickly, maybe every 30 seconds, so getting the sequence of grab QR, decode, copy onto other device, etc. took some finesse).</p>\n<p>Thanks everyone for your assistance!  While it was a long road to get here, I think I finally have a setup that’s at least moderately usable.</p>",
